<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-cn-1366-4/%E9%80%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%9B%A0%E8%A7%A6%E5%AA%92.jpg" alt="逆模因触媒.jpg" class="image" /></div>
