<div class="objclassbar">
<div class="sideleft">
<div><span class="ocb-text">项目编号：</span><span class="ocb-text">SCP-CN-1366</span></div>
<div><span class="ocb-text">项目等级：</span><span class="ocb-text">Keter</span></div>
</div>
<div class="sidemiddle">
<div><span class="ocb-text">负责站点：</span><span class="ocb-text">Site-CN-i</span></div>
<div><span class="ocb-text">项目主管：</span><span class="ocb-text">Dr.Logic</span></div>
<div><span class="ocb-text">首席研究员：</span><span class="ocb-text">Dr.Logic</span></div>
<div><span class="ocb-text">指派特遣队：</span><span class="ocb-text">MTF-Alpha-i（“弑神者”）</span></div>
</div>
<div class="sideright">
<div class="colorbars-container">
<div class="colorbars full"></div>
